                <div>
                    <h3>Integration with the system</h3>
                    <p class="fst-italic">
                        DevToys is made with <i class="bi bi-heart-fill"></i>and designed with to embrace its operating system.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="bi bi-check"></i> Compact Overlay aka. Picture-in-Picture mode</li>
                        <li><i class="bi bi-check"></i> Task Bar's jump list</li>
