                        <li><i class="bi bi-check"></i> Extensible (see our <a href="/doc">SDK and documentation</a>)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="fst-italic">
                        Made with <i class="bi bi-heart-fill"></i>by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/etiennebaudoux/" target="_blank">Etienne Baudoux</a> and <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/benjamin-titeux/" target="_blank">Benjamin Titeux</a>, from Seattle, WA and Paris, France.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
