                <div>
                    <h3>Use it from the Terminal</h3>
                    <p class="fst-italic">
                        DevToys can used from a command line prompt, making it possible to use in new scenarios such as <strong>Continuous Integration</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Most tools that make sense to be used as command prompt are available in <strong>DevToys CLI</strong>. DevToys CLI is a separated app than the one with a GUI. Both are extensible.
                    </p>
